# ReadJson build output (readjson.exe + vendored VC7.1 runtime + test output).
# The /Tools/ReadJson/*.dll line re-ignores the runtime DLLs that line ~22's
# "!/Tools/**/*.dll" exception would otherwise force back in.
Tools/ReadJson/readjson.exe
/Tools/ReadJson/*.dll
Tools/ReadJson/testOutput/
Tools/ReadJson/_conformance.txt
Tools/ReadJson/_render.txt
